Per the CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 attribution requirements (Title, Author, Source, License),
plus the NonCommercial and ShareAlike notices:

* Title:   "Game of Thrones" character relationship graph (84 characters / 216 relations)
* Author:  Andrew Beveridge -- the upstream character-interaction dataset
           "Network of Thrones" (Andrew Beveridge and Jie Shan, Math Horizons, 2016),
           published at https://github.com/mathbeveridge/gameofthrones and reused as
           the creative-track dataset of the Graph Drawing Contest 2018.
